  "text": "## CHUNK 1 — Basic Eligibility Criteria\n\n### Who is eligible to apply for an Axis Bank Credit Card?\n\nTo be eligible for an Axis Bank Credit Card, you must meet the following basic criteria:\n\n- **Age:** Between 18 and 70 years\n- **Citizenship:** Indian resident or Non-Resident Indian (NRI)\n- **Employment:** Salaried or self-employed\n- **Income:** Minimum income requirement varies by card variant\n- **Credit Score:** A CIBIL score of 750 or above is generally preferred\n- **Existing relationship:** Existing Axis Bank account holders may get priority processing\n\n> Axis Bank independently assesses credit risk per RBI guidelines — a high score does not guarantee approval.\n\n---"
