  "text": "## CHUNK 9 — Add-On / Supplementary Cards\n\n### Can I get an add-on credit card for a family member?\n\nYes. Axis Bank offers **add-on (supplementary) cards** for family members.\n\n- **Who qualifies:** Spouse, parents, siblings, or children above 18 years\n- **How to apply:** Request via Axis Mobile App, Internet Banking, or by calling customer care\n- **Limit:** The add-on card shares the primary cardholder's credit limit\n- **Liability:** All spends on add-on cards are billed to the primary cardholder\n- **Benefits:** Add-on cards participate in the same rewards programme as the primary card"
