  "text": "## CHUNK 7 — Foreign Currency Transaction Fee\n\n### What charges apply for international/foreign currency transactions?\n\nWhen you use your Axis Bank credit card for transactions in a foreign currency:\n\n- **Forex Markup Fee:** 3.5% of the transaction amount for most cards\n- **Exceptions:**\n  - Burgundy Private card: Nil forex markup\n  - PRIMUS card: Nil forex markup\n  - Magnus: Reduced forex markup — check card T&C\n\n> Foreign currency transactions are converted to INR using the prevailing exchange rate on the transaction date. The forex markup is charged on the converted INR amount.\n\n---"
