  "title": "Other Fees and Charges",
  "text": "## CHUNK 8 — Other Fees and Charges\n\n### What other fees should I be aware of on my Axis Bank Credit Card?\n\n| Fee Type | Amount |\n|---|---|\n| Over-limit fee | 2.5% of the over-limit amount, min ₹550 |\n| Cheque return / auto-debit failure fee | ₹500 per instance |\n| Card replacement fee | ₹200 – ₹500 (varies by card) |\n| Duplicate statement fee | ₹100 per statement (beyond free period) |\n| Reward redemption fee (EDGE portal) | ₹99 per redemption transaction |\n| Miles / partner loyalty conversion fee | ₹199 per conversion |\n| Rent transaction fee | 1% of the rent transaction amount |\n| Fuel surcharge waiver | 1% surcharge waived at fuel stations for transactions between ₹400–₹4,000 (subject to monthly cap) |\n\n> **Reward Redemption Fee (2025 change):** Effective 2025, a fee of ₹99 is charged for each EDGE Reward redemption and ₹199 for partner miles conversion. This is an important change from the earlier free redemption model.\n\n---"
