  "title": "How to Earn EDGE Reward Points",
  "text": "## CHUNK 2 — How to Earn EDGE Reward Points\n\n### How do I earn EDGE Reward Points on my Axis Bank credit card?\n\nReward points are earned on eligible transactions:\n\n| Card | Base Earn Rate | Accelerated Earn Rate |\n|---|---|---|\n| Rewards Credit Card | 2 pts per ₹125 | 10X on apparel & dept. stores |\n| ACE | Cashback (not points) | 5% on utility via GPay |\n| Magnus | 12 pts per ₹200 | 35 pts/₹200 above ₹1.5L/month |\n| Atlas | EDGE Miles (see CHUNK 6) | Tier-based bonus miles |\n| SELECT | Points per ₹200 | Higher rate on select categories |\n\n**Transactions that typically do NOT earn rewards:**\n- Cash advances (ATM withdrawals)\n- Fuel transactions (at most petrol pumps)\n- Rent payments\n- Wallet reloads\n- Cash-equivalent transactions\n\n---"
