  "title": "Milestone Benefits",
  "text": "## CHUNK 3 — Milestone Benefits\n\n### What are milestone benefits on Axis Bank credit cards?\n\nMilestone benefits are **bonus rewards credited when spending crosses a defined threshold** in a billing cycle or year.\n\n**Rewards Credit Card:**\n- 1,500 EDGE Reward Points on net spends of ₹30,000 per statement cycle\n- Excluded transactions: rent, wallet reloads, fuel, cash withdrawals\n\n**Magnus:**\n- Accelerated rate of 35 EDGE points per ₹200 kicks in when monthly spend exceeds ₹1.5 lakh\n\n**Atlas:**\n- 2,500 EDGE Miles on annual spends of ₹3 lakh (offsets the ₹5,000 annual fee)\n- Higher tier unlocks (Gold, Platinum) with higher milestone thresholds provide more lounge access\n\n**SELECT:**\n- Annual milestone benefits including bonus points or vouchers — refer to your welcome kit for the specific threshold\n\n---"
