  "title": "EDGE Miles (Travel Rewards)",
  "text": "## CHUNK 4 — EDGE Miles (Travel Rewards)\n\n### What are EDGE Miles and how are they different from EDGE Reward Points?\n\n**EDGE Miles** are a specialized reward currency primarily associated with the **Atlas Credit Card** and used for travel-specific redemptions.\n\n- **Earning:** Earned as EDGE Miles instead of EDGE Reward Points on Atlas card spends\n- **Value:** Typically 1 EDGE Mile ≈ ₹1–2 depending on redemption partner\n- **Redemption:** Can be redeemed for flight tickets, hotel bookings, or transferred to partner airline frequent flyer programmes\n\n**Partner Airline Miles Conversion (Atlas card):**\n- Air India Flying Returns\n- InterMiles (Jet Airways partner programme)\n- Singapore Airlines KrisFlyer\n- Vistara Club Vistara (now merged with Air India)\n\n> **Conversion fee (2025):** ₹199 per partner miles conversion transaction\n\n---"
