  "title": "How to Redeem EDGE Reward Points",
  "text": "## CHUNK 5 — How to Redeem EDGE Reward Points\n\n### How can I redeem my Axis Bank EDGE Reward Points?\n\n**Redemption channels:**\n1. **EDGE Rewards Portal:** Visit edgerewards.axisbank.com → Log in → Browse catalogue → Redeem\n2. **Axis Mobile App:** Go to Cards → Manage Rewards → Redeem Points\n3. **Customer Care:** Call 1860-419-5555 and request redemption\n\n**Redemption options:**\n- **Product Catalogue:** Electronics, appliances, lifestyle products\n- **E-Vouchers:** Amazon, Flipkart, Swiggy, Uber, etc.\n- **Cashback:** Credited directly to your card outstanding\n- **Airmiles:** Transfer to partner airline/hotel loyalty programmes\n- **Hotel/Flight Bookings:** Book directly via EDGE portal using points\n- **Partner Outlets:** At select merchant locations\n\n**Redemption Fee (2025 update):**\n- ₹99 per redemption transaction on the EDGE portal\n- ₹199 for conversion to partner loyalty programmes\n\n**Minimum points required:** 300 EDGE Reward Points\n\n---"
