  "text": "## CHUNK 6 — Cashback vs Reward Points\n\n### What is the difference between cashback and reward points on Axis Bank cards?\n\n| Feature | Cashback (ACE, Flipkart) | Reward Points (Rewards, Magnus, SELECT) |\n|---|---|---|\n| Form | Direct credit to card outstanding | Points credited to EDGE account |\n| Redemption | Automatic (no action needed) | Must redeem via EDGE portal or app |\n| Value | Exact ₹ value (5% = 5 paise per rupee) | Variable (1 point = ₹0.20 typically) |\n| Redemption Fee | None | ₹99 per redemption (2025) |\n| Flexibility | Lower — fixed to cash savings | Higher — products, travel, vouchers |\n| Best for | Users who want simplicity | Users who want travel/product variety |\n\n---"
