  "text": "## CHUNK 8 — Other Card Benefits\n\n### What other benefits do Axis Bank credit cards offer?\n\n**Common benefits across premium cards:**\n- **Fuel Surcharge Waiver:** 1% surcharge waived at fuel stations for transactions between ₹400–₹4,000 (subject to a monthly cap of ₹500)\n- **Dining Offers:** Discounts at partner restaurants via Axis Bank dining programme\n- **Shopping Offers:** Exclusive discounts at Axis Bank partner merchants (Amazon, Myntra, Nykaa, etc.)\n- **Insurance Benefits:** Personal accident cover, lost card liability cover (varies by card)\n- **Concierge Services:** Available on Magnus, SELECT, and other premium cards\n- **Golf Programme:** Complimentary golf rounds at select courses (SELECT, Magnus, Premium cards)\n- **Annual Memberships:** Worth ₹1,000 per year on Rewards Credit Card (e.g., Swiggy One, Zomato Gold)\n\n---"
