  "title": "Auto-Debit Facility",
  "text": "## CHUNK 4 — Auto-Debit Facility\n\n### How do I set up auto-debit for my Axis Bank Credit Card?\n\nAuto-debit automatically deducts your credit card bill from a linked Axis Bank savings/current account on the due date.\n\n**How to set up:**\n1. Log in to Axis Mobile App or Internet Banking\n2. Go to Credit Card → Settings → Auto Pay\n3. Choose auto-debit option:\n   - **Full Outstanding Balance** (recommended — avoids all interest)\n   - **Minimum Amount Due**\n   - **Fixed Custom Amount**\n4. Link your Axis Bank account and confirm\n\n**Benefits:**\n- Ensures payment is never missed\n- Prevents late payment fees\n- Protects your CIBIL score\n\n> Auto-debit from a **non-Axis bank account** can be set up via NACH mandate — request the form at a branch or via customer care.\n\n---"
