  "title": "Zero-Cost / No-Cost EMI",
  "text": "## CHUNK 6 — Zero-Cost / No-Cost EMI\n\n### What is no-cost EMI on Axis Bank credit cards?\n\n**No-cost EMI (0% EMI)** is available at select partner merchants where the interest cost is absorbed by the merchant or Axis Bank as a promotional offer.\n\n- **How it works:** You pay only the principal in monthly instalments — no interest\n- **Availability:** Online platforms (Flipkart, Amazon, Myntra), offline retail stores\n- **Processing fee:** A processing fee may apply (₹199–₹499 + GST) — check the specific offer\n- **Eligibility:** Depends on the merchant, purchase amount, and card type\n\n> During no-cost EMI periods, GST on interest may still be charged in some cases — verify before opting in.\n\n---"
