  "title": "Balance Transfer",
  "text": "## CHUNK 7 — Balance Transfer\n\n### Can I transfer my balance from another credit card to my Axis Bank card?\n\nYes. Axis Bank offers a **Balance Transfer (BT)** facility to transfer outstanding balances from other banks' credit cards to your Axis Bank credit card at a lower interest rate.\n\n- **Purpose:** Consolidate high-interest debt from other cards at a lower promotional rate\n- **Typical BT Rate:** Lower than standard finance charges — promotional rate varies by offer\n- **Tenure:** Usually 3–12 months\n- **Minimum Transfer Amount:** ₹5,000 typically\n- **Processing Fee:** 1–2% of the transferred amount, or as per specific offer terms\n\n**How to apply:**\n- Contact Axis Bank customer care at 1860-419-5555\n- Log in to Internet Banking → Credit Card → Balance Transfer → Apply\n\n> Interest charges apply from the transfer date. Evaluate the total cost (processing fee + interest) before transferring.\n\n---"
