  "title": "Virtual Credit Card",
  "text": "## CHUNK 5 — Virtual Credit Card\n\n### Does Axis Bank offer a virtual credit card?\n\nYes. Axis Bank provides a **virtual credit card** for secure online transactions.\n\n- **What it is:** A temporary card number with a limited validity period generated for a specific online transaction\n- **Purpose:** Protects your actual card number from being exposed to merchants\n- **How to generate:** Axis Mobile App → Cards → Virtual Card → Generate\n\n> Virtual cards are particularly useful for first-time purchases on new or untrusted websites.\n\n---"
