  "title": "Changing Personal Details",
  "text": "## CHUNK 6 — Changing Personal Details\n\n### How do I update my address, mobile number, or email on my Axis Bank Credit Card?\n\n**Mobile Number Update:**\n- Must be done at an Axis Bank branch with ID proof (cannot be changed digitally for security reasons)\n\n**Email Address Update:**\n1. Axis Mobile App → Profile → Contact Details → Update Email\n2. Internet Banking → Settings → Update Email\n3. Customer care: 1860-419-5555\n\n**Address Update:**\n1. Axis Mobile App → Profile → Address → Update\n2. Internet Banking\n3. Branch visit with address proof (Aadhaar/utility bill)\n\n**Important:** Keep your contact details updated to ensure you receive transaction alerts, OTPs, and statements without interruption.\n\n---"
